WEBVTT

30:27.860 --> 30:29.840 line:80%
They must be up to no good.

30:29.960 --> 30:32.490 line:80%
I say we report
to the officials immediately.

30:32.760 --> 30:35.820 line:80%
Judging by his looks,
he doesn't seem like a bad person.

30:35.830 --> 30:38.230 line:80%
Villains don't have labels on their faces.
